forces the tail below $\varepsilon_{\rm far}$. Thus
\[ \delta(\sigma_0)\ \ge\ \min\{\delta_S(\sigma_0),\ \mu_\star(\sigma_0)/2\}\ -\ \varepsilon_{\rm far}. \]

