Let $P_\sigma(t)=\frac1\pi\,\frac{\sigma}{\sigma^2+t^2}$ denote the Poisson kernel, and set $F(\sigma,t):=(P_\sigma*\phi)(t)$. For a fixed cone aperture $\alpha$ (as in the main text), the Lusin area function is
